<bibRefCitation id="9201C5E2FF94414DFF3C26744B79FEFA" author="Sziraki, G." box="[151,309,324,350]" pageId="14" pageNumber="415" pagination="57 - 72" refId="ref28571" refString="Sziraki, G. (1998) An annotated checklist of the Ascalaphidae species known from Asia and from the Pacific Islands. Folia Entomologica Hungarica, 59, 57 - 72. [BotN ref  9362]" type="journal article" year="1998">Sziráki (1998)</bibRefCitation>
